				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p198662">Re: Concept for actually making VIN useful - &quot;MBC-5B&quot;</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=198662#p198662"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Jun 21, 2017 12:46 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
